wminc-fs-signup-text: Ka fooŋ taa a toma yuori, sɔrɔɔ [$1 kyɛ kpɛ]. Ka fooŋ ba taa kaŋa meŋ , de [$2 maale kaŋa]. O ba dirɛ a wagere a maaloŋ poɔ.
wminc-fs-settings-text:
Aayi gaa [[Special:Preferences#mw-htmlform-i18n|your preferences]]kyɛ leɛre a sɛgrɛ a wiki tɛɛsi poɔ. A dɛŋdɛŋ soba la fo Kɔkɔre, onaŋ la ka fo de a fo dɛŋdɛŋ piiloŋ, kyɛ foŋ baŋ leɛ o la.
A ayi soba a toma na fo naŋ boɔrɔ ka fo toŋ ane a ata soba meŋ la a Kɔkɔre bie.
Ka fooŋ ba baŋ a bie ama, sɔrɔɔ la gaa [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|manual]] bee sɔɔre a [[{{MediaWiki:Portal-url}}|help]].
wminc-fs-userpage-text: Pampana ŋa maale for meŋɛ tontoŋ gampɛle $1 ne yelbilee mine fo tɔɔraa. Fo meŋ na kaa la a tage lammo zie a saazu a gampɛle poɔ.
wminc-fs-startwiki-text: A fo aroozie a wiki e la $1. Fo naŋ baŋ piili la a wiki maaloo gampɛle meŋɛ maaloŋ a $2.
wminc-fs-startwiki-exists-text:
A fo wiki prefix la $1. A gampɛle meŋɛ e la $2. Fo na baŋ yeli la yɛlɛ a land gbuli deɛ poɔ!
Ka fooŋ boɔra ka fo maale gampɛle, sɛge a fo yuori a yoe bɔ zie a saazu, kyɛ tu a tage lammo merɛ.
